_sText:
~Omaha_Beach~
This map is probably the most fun map to ever be created in any WWII game so I decided  to create it in CS:S. The CT's start in the water and boats, while the T's spawn on the other side right by the bunkers. The whole objective is just kill the other team.
This is my second CSS map.
To install this map extract the .BSP file to go to your 
Valve>Steam>SteamApps>*yourloginname*>counter-strike source>cstrike>maps folder
I hope you like this map, it took a long time to do, I'm currently working on making trenches behind the bunkers so stay tuned if you want trenches!

Enjoy!
